commands.enchant.failed.category: Enchantments have been applied but the enchantment category failed to sync to the client.
container.enchiridion.siphon.sculk_catal: Use a Sculk Catalyst to add experience points
dataPack.enchiridion.vanilla_balancing.d: Modifies Enchiridion content to fit vanilla's balancing.
death.attack.enchiridion.whirlpool.item: %1$s was caught in a whirlpool while fighting %2$s wielding %3$s
death.attack.enchiridion.whirlpool.playe: %1$s was caught in a whirlpool while fighting %2$s
enchantment.enchiridion.agile.desc: Allows the user to sprint at a reduced speed whilst using items.
enchantment.enchiridion.agile.descriptio: An enchantment that allows the user to sprint at a reduced speed whilst using items.
enchantment.enchiridion.ashes_curse.desc: Sets drops from this item on fire.
A curse that sets item drops obtained from this tool or weapon on fire.
enchantment.enchiridion.barding.desc: Reduces damage towards the mob you are riding.
enchantment.enchiridion.barding.descript: An enchantment that reduces any damage towards the mob you are riding.
enchantment.enchiridion.beheading.desc: Adds a chance to obtain a mob's head when used to kill a mob.
enchantment.enchiridion.beheading.descri: An enchantment that provides a chance for mobs killed by this weapon to drop their heads.
enchantment.enchiridion.circuit.desc: Allows the user to sprint in any direction.
enchantment.enchiridion.circuit.descript: An enchantment that allows the user to sprint in any direction.
enchantment.enchiridion.cleaving.desc: Increases the duration that shields are disabled for by this item and slightly increases damage.
enchantment.enchiridion.cleaving.descrip: An enchantment that increases the duration that shields get disabled for and slightly increases damage with this Axe.
enchantment.enchiridion.climber.descript: An enchantment that increases the climbing speed of the user.
enchantment.enchiridion.coyote.desc: Allows the user to briefly walk on air after leaving the ground.
enchantment.enchiridion.coyote.descripti: An enchantment that allows the user to briefly walk on air after leaving the ground.
enchantment.enchiridion.crumble.desc: Natural stones are mined faster and do not drop items.
enchantment.enchiridion.crumble.descript: An enchantment that makes this Pickaxe mine natural stones faster at the cost of the blocks not dropping.
enchantment.enchiridion.dredge.desc: Adds a chance to fish up an extra item while fishing.
enchantment.enchiridion.dredge.descripti: An enchantment that adds a chance to fish up an extra item while fishing with this Fishing Rod.
enchantment.enchiridion.earthquake.desc: Increases the area of and damages entities caught in the smash attack.
enchantment.enchiridion.earthquake.descr: An enchantment that increases the area of and damages other entities caught in this Mace's smash attack.
enchantment.enchiridion.exhilarating.des: Prevents the user from using up hunger from mining blocks.
An enchantment that prevents the user from using up hunger from mining blocks with this tool.
enchantment.enchiridion.experienced.desc: Fishing with this fishing rod grants more experience.
An enchantment that grants more experience from fishing with this Fishing Rod.
enchantment.enchiridion.flurry.desc: Increases movement speed on snow and ice blocks and reduces friction while sneaking on ice.
enchantment.enchiridion.flurry.descripti: An enchantment that moderately increases the speed that you move on Snow and Ice, and reduces the friction of Ice whilst sneaking.
enchantment.enchiridion.gatling.desc: Automatically fires arrows while using this item.
enchantment.enchiridion.gatling.descript: An enchantment that makes this Bow automatically fire arrows.
enchantment.enchiridion.longshot.desc: Allows you to increase the velocity and accuracy of a fired projectile by holding the Bow at full charge for longer.
enchantment.enchiridion.longshot.descrip: An enchantment that allows you to increase the velocity and accuracy of a fired projectile by holding the Bow at full charge for longer.
enchantment.enchiridion.murky_waters_cur: Significantly increases the chances of catching junk while fishing.
A curse that increases the chances of catching junk whilst fishing with this Fishing Rod
enchantment.enchiridion.prospector.desc: Adds a chance to obtain valuables after digging up dirt, sand or gravel.
enchantment.enchiridion.prospector.descr: An enchantment that adds a chance to obtain valuables after digging up dirt, sand or gravel with this Shovel.
enchantment.enchiridion.reach.desc: Increases block interaction range of the tool.
enchantment.enchiridion.reach.descriptio: An enchantment that increases the block interaction range of this tool.
enchantment.enchiridion.reliability.desc: Increases the enchantment quality and durability of fished up items.
An enchantment that increases the enchantment quality and durability of fished up items from this Fishing Rod.
enchantment.enchiridion.snow_strike.desc: Causes additional freeze damage and slower movement when used to attack a mob.
An enchantment that makes this weapon's attacks slow enemies' movement and take freeze damage for a short duration.
enchantment.enchiridion.splitting.desc: Splits logs into more planks than what crafting would give.
enchantment.enchiridion.splitting.descri: An enchantment that causes this Axe to split dropped logs into planks.
enchantment.enchiridion.sticky.desc: Allows the user to climb blocks for a short amount of time.
enchantment.enchiridion.sticky.descripti: An enchantment that allows the user to climb blocks for a short amount of time.
enchantment.enchiridion.tailwind.desc: Launches you forward when attacking with.
enchantment.enchiridion.tailwind.descrip: An enchantment that launches you forward when attacking with this weapon.
enchantment.enchiridion.vaulting.desc: Increases jump height based on movement speed.
enchantment.enchiridion.vaulting.descrip: An enchantment that increases the user's jump height based on movement speed.
enchantment.enchiridion.whirlpool.desc: Creates a damaging whirlpool around the user.
enchantment.enchiridion.whirlpool.descri: An enchantment that creates a damaging whirlpool around this Trident's user whilst using it.
lore.enchiridion.siphoning_table: A block that allows players to craft enchantments using items, Lapis Lazuli and Experience Points sourced from Sculk Catalysts.
resourcePack.enchiridion.enchanted_books: Modifies Enchanted Book textures for Enchiridion.
